data.description: This 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Two Story home on Bloomington’s south side has recently been remodeled and shows like an almost new home on the inside! Other improvements include the forced air gas furnace, the gas water heater and roof. You will enjoy living on a cul-de-sac with a privacy fenced rear yard, and sitting on the large covered front porch that adds to the great curb appeal! The kitchen has been recently redesigned with additional cabinets/counter and looks new! In the kitchen you will notice the soft close cabinets/drawers, granite counter tops, backsplash, and stainless appliances. The bathrooms have also been updated and the primary bath includes a tiled shower. Yes, the flooring and painting have also been done! Conveniently located on Bloomington’s south side near Kroger South, Bloomington Country Club, Bachelor Middle School, the Post Office in Clear Creek, the Iron Pit Gym and walking trails. This location is also a quick drive to downtown Bloomington, Indiana University, and a few minutes to I-69. Included in the sale - refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, gas range, microwave, washer, dryer, blinds, shed and projector/screen in the Living Room.
